{"tid":2133880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(討論)私人市場人工跌,樓市keep住升","createTime":"2020-07-31T10:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T10:50:30.000Z","uid":98860,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a2855e1a85d1f6f9decc85796a875212d0d97c11","tid":2133880,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:46:31.000Z","msg":"私人市場人工跌, 樓市keep住升,<br />\n<br />\n樓價唔計你升得多當一年3-4%<br />\n平均600-800萬樓一年已經升24萬至32萬<br />\n<br />\n當你人工一畢業3萬咁叻仔一年儲人工6成, 都係得21萬😹 升幅都未追到。每年加一至兩千人工都未夠追樓價。 <br />\n<br />\n香港各行各業發展仲要愈黎愈差, 赤化問題嚴重。以往神科都漸失光彩,今年開始大部份狀元出國發展, 學歷貶值,遲下碩士等於學士。 付出大量時間同錢, 面對劇烈競爭。。。<br />\n<br />\n年輕一代點自處?<br />\n<br />\n利申:說服緊條女唔好生仔,安安穩穩早啲退休好過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbbdf17218959da6103e32002ccffc5470c9a62","tid":2133880,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"有能力既留低，無能力既返肇慶置業"},{"pid":"48410004ad20f265a43f8b597c11a354d9bbd7ff","tid":2133880,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43f9ead2cd9f818692101396590956c29592b62a","tid":2133880,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"公屋"},{"pid":"e15554313f16fe88e48426a6b95c664c6b4a419d","tid":2133880,"uid":3967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"移民走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d227c735f4a63089abdbbc968aa52d1e578069","tid":2133880,"uid":123765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"你條女咩料，仲諗緊生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cadedc250d1b439f0c65d0f0ad7afe799a541e","tid":2133880,"uid":291487,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"因為持樓既大多數都係 支那種"},{"pid":"7bea3154bb8279bc25d98f9fa1a16802d2e9287c","tid":